    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-table_cell-7a642360c0-1",
      "kind": "table_cell",
      "text": "Celeste Neuffer",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-table_cell-b061f0df81-1",
      "kind": "table_cell",
      "text": "Seattle, WA",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-table_cell-5f20a6b42b-1",
      "kind": "table_cell",
      "text": "Events",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-table_cell-15efd8d9bf-1",
      "kind": "table_cell",
      "text": "Len Englund",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-table_cell-000c311f2d-2",
      "kind": "table_cell",
      "text": "Bellevue, WA",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-paragraph-873c8a7099-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Meetings were selected to be held on each second Monday of each month. A charter was applied for from the US ORIENTEERING FEDERATION and was granted prior to the following meeting.",
      "text_length": 180
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-paragraph-07691345d6-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "At the second meeting, a dues structure was discussed. A $4 for individual and $7 family rate was approved.",
      "text_length": 107
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1978-01_02-paragraph-3f3f93f4d9-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "We have a lot of ground to cover to become a solid club. Come out and join us at the meets. If you feel like adding to your store of knowledge, help us or set up a meet.",
      "text_length": 169
    },
    {
